                  "content": "Action feedbacks should be communicated, and disappear automatically. \n[book title] marked as completed, marked as not started, deleted, updated",
                  "fontFamily": "Geist Mono",
                  "fontSize": 12,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}